{"tid":2167314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【美國大選】共和黨逾70名前國安官員表態支持拜登  ！","createTime":"2020-08-21T04:43:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T07:18:50.000Z","uid":91914,"like":17,"dislike":182,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"d673355d05b14be406c3fc5ea642321c8a71ace5","tid":2167314,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:43:37.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨總統候選人拜登（Joe Biden）即將發表接受提名演說。共和黨逾70名前國家安全官員8月20日發布聯署的公開信，表態支持拜登，其中包括中央情報局前局長和聯邦調查局前局長。<br />\n73名前官員組成名為「支持拜登的共和黨前國家安全官員」的小組，成員包括曾服務列根（Ronald Reagan）、老布殊（George H.W. Bush）、小布殊（George W. Bush ）和特朗普（Donald Trump）政府的官員，例如曾任中情局和聯邦調查局局長的韋伯斯特（William Webster）。<br />\n<br />\n他們批評特朗普缺乏領導國家所需的性格和能力，腐敗的行為反映不適合擔當總統。他們認為，特朗普辜負了國家，前副總統拜登應該獲選為下任美國總統。他們同時不滿特朗普疏遠海外盟友，無力應對疫情以及對種族問題示威的反應。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨舉行全國代表大會期間，多名共和黨重量級人物發言，「倒伐」支持拜登，包括前國務卿鮑威爾（Colin Powell）、俄亥俄州前州長卡西奇（John Kasich）和新澤西州前州長惠特曼（Christine Todd Whitman）。<br />\n<br />\nHK01"},{"pid":"af998a4ddf4e67c04fc0db54c22847fd20437186","tid":2167314,"uid":183758,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:44:40.000Z","msg":"全部共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d530f9dea6b3716814f64234ea329fed6057d947","tid":2167314,"uid":91914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026fbf3ab56f02c019db5d98f157cc317e4d06b8","tid":2167314,"uid":289946,"like":10,"dislike":7,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:45:33.000Z","msg":"侵侵今次無了。。。"},{"pid":"fd2cda374458a5b2406d15070407e6b2ef1db638","tid":2167314,"uid":4783,"like":36,"dislike":3,"scor